    .col.s6.left-align
      %p.home-text-paragraph
        The Dead Artists community gets frequent project updates on Twitter and Discord.
      %p.home-text-paragraph.m.l
        We will give you a platform to talk about your favorite paintings, artists or NFTs.
      %p.home-text-paragraph.l
        Join our Discord and get in touch with the team.
